86 template <class Interface>
87 bool TMultiReferenceMember<Interface>::EnsureInitialized() const
88 {
89  bool retVal = false;
90 
91  if (!m_isInitialized && (m_definitionComponentPtr != NULL) && BaseClass::IsValid()){
92  const ICompositeComponent* parentPtr = m_definitionComponentPtr->GetParentComponent();
93  if (parentPtr != NULL){
94  int attributesCount = BaseClass::GetCount();
95 
96  m_components.resize(attributesCount);
97 
98  retVal = true;
99 
100  for (int i = 0; i < attributesCount; ++i){
101  const QByteArray& componentId = BaseClass::operator[](i);
102 
103  QByteArray baseId;
104  QByteArray subId;
105  BaseClass2::SplitId(componentId, baseId, subId);
106 
107  IComponent* componentPtr = parentPtr->GetSubcomponent(baseId);
108 
109  m_components[i] = BaseClass2::ExtractInterface<Interface>(componentPtr, subId);
110  }
111 
112  m_isInitialized = retVal;
113  }
114  else{
115  qCritical("Components are is defined, but definition component has no parent");
116  }
117  }
118 
119  return m_isInitialized;
120 }
